snippet.title: Slendrina Must Die: The Forest
snippet.description:
Play Online: http://www.danygames.com/play/adventure/slendrina-must-die-the-forest.html
Android Download: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PoisonGames.SlendrinaMustDieTheForest
PC Download: https://gamejolt.com/games/SMDTheForest/313628

Find out the dark secret that Slendrina hides in the Forest.
You need to find seven keys to unlock the secret!
Watch out for Slendrina, her mother and her child!
They are keeping the secret and guard it with their lives.
Good luck!

Features:
- Awesome 3D Graphics
- Easy Controls
- Well known Poison Games Gameplay
- Scary Game with Firearms!

* Five weapons:
- Brass Knuckles
- M9 Handgun
- Shotgun
- RPK Light Machine Gun
- M67 Frag Grenade

Game is based on Slendrina: The Forest
